---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy — Georgetown Jerseys"
  description="Privacy policy for Georgetown Jerseys website."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container privacy-content">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <h2>Who We Are</h2>
      <p>Georgetown Jerseys is a sports uniform and custom apparel shop located at 103 E Main St #2, Georgetown, MA 01833. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our website.</p>

      <h2>What We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect information that you voluntarily provide through:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Order form:</strong> Name, email, phone number, team details, and order preferences. This information is sent to us via email and stored in our form processing service (Netlify).</li>
        <li><strong>Newsletter signup:</strong> Email address only, stored by our email service provider (Mailchimp).</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Website Analytics</h2>
      <p>We use privacy-friendly analytics to understand how visitors use our site. This data is aggregated and anonymous — we do not track individual visitors, use cookies for analytics, or share data with advertising networks.</p>

      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To respond to your order inquiry and process your team's uniform order</li>
        <li>To send you seasonal updates if you subscribed to our newsletter</li>
        <li>To improve our website and services</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

      <h2>Where Your Data Is Stored</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Form submissions:</strong> Processed and stored by Netlify (netlify.com). Submissions are also sent to us via email.</li>
        <li><strong>Newsletter emails:</strong> Stored by Mailchimp (mailchimp.com) on their servers.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You can request to see, update, or delete your personal information at any time by contacting us at <a href="mailto:orders@gtownjerseys.com">orders@gtownjerseys.com</a> or calling <a href="tel:+19783528240">(978) 352-8240</a>.</p>
      <p>To unsubscribe from our newsletter, use the unsubscribe link at the bottom of any email.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, contact us:</p>
      <p>
        Georgetown Jerseys<br />
        103 E Main St #2, Georgetown, MA 01833<br />
        <a href="tel:+19783528240">(978) 352-8240</a><br />
        <a href="mailto:orders@gtownjerseys.com">orders@gtownjerseys.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .privacy-content {
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .privacy-content h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .updated {
    color: var(--color-neutral-600);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .privacy-content h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    margin-top: var(--space-8);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .privacy-content ul {
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .privacy-content li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    color: var(--color-neutral-600);
  }

  .privacy-content p {
    color: var(--color-neutral-600);
  }
</style>
